<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Abraham's Blog</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/</link><description/><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.inshomepgup.com/tags/nvm/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>NVM 在 Windows 端的使用（Nodejs 环境配置）</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/language/nodejs/nvm/nvm-%E5%9C%A8windows%E7%AB%AF%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8nodejs%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/language/nodejs/nvm/nvm-%E5%9C%A8windows%E7%AB%AF%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8nodejs%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</guid><description>&lt;p>记录一下我的日常
从官网下载nodejs 并安装&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://nodejs.org/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>nodejs&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>下载nvm 并安装&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/coreybutler/nvm-windows" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>nvm&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>配置nvm的node源和npm源&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">8
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 腾讯&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">nvm npm_mirror http://mirrors.cloud.tencent.com/npm/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">nvm node_mirror https://mirrors.cloud.tencent.com/nodejs-release/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 阿里&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">nvm npm_mirror https://npmmirror.com/mirrors/npm/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">nvm node_mirror https://npmmirror.com/mirrors/node/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 顺便设置一下腾讯的npm源&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">npm config &lt;span class="nb">set&lt;/span> registry http://mirrors.cloud.tencent.com/npm/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description><category>backend</category><category>nodejs</category><category>nvm</category><category>nodejs</category><category>windows</category></item><item><title>NVM 的简单使用</title><link>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/language/nodejs/nvm/nvm%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.inshomepgup.com/programming/language/nodejs/nvm/nvm%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</guid><description>&lt;p>配置好了 nvm 以及对应的 node 源以后可以快乐的使用各个版本的 nodejs 了。
nvm 在不同的平台上表现还是不一样的。
Windows use 以后在后续的终端里也是会维持之前的版本。
Mac 这边需要单独配置以后才能设为默认版本，不然都会使用默认版本。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>不得不说近几年的 nodejs 版本有点像 java 的版本一样，疯狂的升级，不过我印象里之前最坚挺的还是 node16 的版本。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">9
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">nvm install &lt;span class="m">22&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1">#安装 nodejs 22 版本&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">nvm install &lt;span class="m">20&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1"># 安装 20 的版本&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">nvm ls-remote &lt;span class="c1"># 查看远程的所有版本&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">nvm &lt;span class="nb">alias&lt;/span> default &lt;span class="m">18&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1"># 设置默认的版本，终端的默认版本&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">nvm use &lt;span class="m">20&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1"># 使用 20 的版本&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description><category>backend</category><category>nodejs</category><category>nvm</category><category>nodejs</category></item></channel></rss>